Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出动诺伦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.51,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(718,663)}Norn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才刚觉醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是查探对方想法的程度还行
