Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3 第4磁冠护盾展开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场形成完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺伦与敌方欧西亚型开始交战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与彦岛距离 5000
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考联系完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有机体维持现位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？剑司学长负责系统？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的头目就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都要平安归还
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能损失一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想法太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙负责初次遇敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁在远程操作无人机？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心你们自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人学习了岛的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈班程序 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用剑决胜负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太犯规了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
