Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合各人的特性改变了战术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后 天照 改变地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特性…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只要打倒1只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能解决全部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你退后了
