Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能让一骑和总士战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner部队已崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要战斗力保证分离区域和撤退 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是这样而已
