Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芹 镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 救我…剑司学长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作再快点 再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能…给我把武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 停止了多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能动的有3架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ALVIS内发生未知力场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人吗 地点在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙骨区
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙骨区？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动三号机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了开发无人机 整个系统都重新制作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二号机重新启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么…还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…像一骑学长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里来的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器从格纳库消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有弹射出的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机体的结晶核…结晶核在增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner所有机体 战斗继续
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格纳库报告称机体结晶核引发了未知现象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是你们所希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并让我觉醒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你们而存在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实点 亡灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我力量…支配这怪物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…解除了怪物的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认Nicht与Sein启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sein…觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二号机 维持现位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余各机交换位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换敌人 保护同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都要生还
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要守护岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会守住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动手臂上闪耀戈班印记之时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传承之魂正是不屈之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超必杀 戈班闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画看太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要我像一骑学长一样战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头目出马了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的愿望只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是长久的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而为此我们所获得的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却总是背离和平的力量
